occurrences.\n\n   **Latency Spike**: ~7x increase (97,100 / 13,679). Indicates bottleneck between `checkoutservice` and `paymentservice`.\n\n2. **Trace from `frontend` → `hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder` (Checkoutservice-0 on `aiops-k8s-04` interacting with other frontend pods):**\n   - **Anomaly Counts and Operation Delays**: Exceeds normal bounds across multiple pods.\n   - **Normal vs Anomaly Duration**: Durations in the range 144,331 ms → 294,339 ms (over 2x).\n\n3. **Redis Cart Interaction Delays**:\n   - `Redis (`aiops-k8s-07`) had latency anomalies when called by `cart` and `checkout`.\n\n---\n\n### Correlation\n- Significant latency spikes are isolated to node `aiops-k8s-04`'s `checkoutservice-0` and adjacent interactions with `paymentservice-2`. This aligns with memory pressure signatures reported by Metric Expert.\n\n### Initial Stance\n`SUPPORT` that node `aiops-k8s-04` issues correlate strongly with observed anomalies and delays.\n\n### JSON Output\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"Severe memory pressure aligns with checkoutservice delays, particularly in PaymentService interactions.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Checkoutservice operations saw latency multiplying by ~7x, hosted on node `aiops-k8s-04`, correlating with reported memory anomalies.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased pod CPU usage correlates with delays beyond reasonable thresholds.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PaymentService operations on checkout experienced latency multiplication, linked back to both memory and CPU constraints.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
